en.title: FE Welcomes Quantum Bracelet User, Mayor Rodrigo Duterte of Davao City, Philippines!
en.content:
FE Leader Kenneth Lee Explaining the Benefits of FE's Scalar Energy Products as he Presents Mayor Rody Duterte of Davao City, Philippines with a Quantum Pendant and a Quantum Bracelet.
Kenneth Lee with Mayor Duterte and Organising Chairman of the Tournament, Mr. Ed Bangayan
(on the Mayor's right) and Mr Robert Ynson.		  
 
Mayor Rody Duterte Proudly Wearing his Quantum Bracelet During his Speech at the Awarding
Ceremony of the 10th MEDSA Mayor's Gawad
Kalinga Golf Tournament Cup, Davao City.
